#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:2
msgid "Filesystem Backend"
msgstr "文件系统后端"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:4
msgid ""
"The filesystem backend uses ``FSConnector`` to store LMCache remote "
"chunks as files under one or more POSIX filesystem directories. It is "
"useful when you want a simple persistent remote backend, or when multiple"
" inference workers can see the same mounted directory through local disk,"
" NFS, a parallel filesystem, or a container volume."
msgstr "文件系统后端使用 ``FSConnector`` 将 LMCache 远程块存储为一个或多个 POSIX 文件系统目录下的文件。当您需要一个简单的持久远程后端，或者当多个推理工作者可以通过本地磁盘、NFS、并行文件系统或容器卷查看相同的挂载目录时，它非常有用。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:10
msgid ""
"This backend is different from :doc:`local_storage`. Local disk "
"offloading is a per-process local tier configured through ``local_disk``."
" ``FSConnector`` is a remote backend configured through "
"``remote_storage_plugins`` or the legacy ``remote_url`` field, so it "
"participates in the same remote backend path as Redis, S3, Mooncake, and "
"other remote connectors."
msgstr "该后端与 :doc:`local_storage` 不同。本地磁盘卸载是通过 ``local_disk`` 配置的每个进程本地层。``FSConnector`` 是通过 ``remote_storage_plugins`` 或遗留的 ``remote_url`` 字段配置的远程后端，因此它参与与 Redis、S3、Mooncake 和其他远程连接器相同的远程后端路径。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:17
msgid "When to use it"
msgstr "何时使用它"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:19
msgid "Use ``FSConnector`` when:"
msgstr "使用 ``FSConnector`` 当："

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:21
msgid ""
"You need a lightweight persistent remote backend for development, "
"examples, or benchmark runs."
msgstr "您需要一个轻量级的持久远程后端，用于开发、示例或基准测试。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:23
msgid "Multiple LMCache or vLLM processes share a mounted cache directory."
msgstr "多个 LMCache 或 vLLM 进程共享一个挂载的缓存目录。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:24
msgid ""
"Your storage is already exposed as a filesystem and does not need a "
"separate object-store or key-value service."
msgstr "您的存储已经作为文件系统暴露，不需要单独的对象存储或键值服务。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:26
msgid ""
"You want to test remote-backend behavior before moving to a production "
"backend such as Redis, Valkey, S3, Mooncake, or InfiniStore."
msgstr "您希望在迁移到生产后端（如 Redis、Valkey、S3、Mooncake 或 InfiniStore）之前测试远程后端的行为。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:29
msgid "Avoid using it when:"
msgstr "避免在以下情况下使用它："

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:31
msgid "The filesystem is not shared by every process that must read the cache."
msgstr "当文件系统未被每个必须读取缓存的进程共享时，请避免使用它。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:32
msgid ""
"You need object-store semantics, cross-region persistence, or service-"
"level access control."
msgstr "您需要对象存储语义、跨区域持久性或服务级访问控制。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:34
msgid ""
"The storage path is on a slow network filesystem and sits on the hot "
"request path."
msgstr "存储路径位于一个慢速网络文件系统上，并处于热请求路径上。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:38
msgid "Recommended configuration"
msgstr "推荐配置"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:40
msgid ""
"The recommended form is the built-in remote storage plugin configuration."
" The plugin name ``fs`` selects ``FSConnector`` and the base path is "
"configured in ``extra_config``."
msgstr "推荐的形式是内置的远程存储插件配置。插件名称 ``fs`` 选择 ``FSConnector``，基本路径在 ``extra_config`` 中配置。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:58
msgid ""
"``FSConnector`` creates the base directory if it does not already exist. "
"Each cache chunk is written as a ``.data`` file whose name is derived "
"from the LMCache cache key."
msgstr "``FSConnector`` 会在目录不存在时创建基础目录。每个缓存块作为 ``.data`` 文件写入，其名称源自 LMCache 缓存键。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:63
msgid "Multiple filesystem instances"
msgstr "多个文件系统实例"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:65
msgid ""
"You can configure multiple named ``fs`` instances by appending an "
"instance name after the connector type. The part before the first dot is "
"still the connector type; the full plugin name becomes the "
"``extra_config`` prefix."
msgstr "您可以通过在连接器类型后附加实例名称来配置多个命名的 ``fs`` 实例。在第一个点之前的部分仍然是连接器类型；完整的插件名称成为 ``extra_config`` 前缀。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:77
msgid ""
"This is useful when a deployment wants separate filesystem-backed remote "
"stores for different cache policies, traffic classes, or experiments."
msgstr "当一个部署希望为不同的缓存策略、流量类别或实验提供独立的基于文件系统的远程存储时，这非常有用。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:81
msgid "Multiple base paths"
msgstr "多个基础路径"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:83
msgid ""
"``remote_storage_plugin.<name>.base_path`` may contain a comma-separated "
"list of directories. The connector chooses a directory by hashing the "
"cache chunk key, which spreads files across the configured paths."
msgstr "``remote_storage_plugin.<name>.base_path`` 可以包含一个以逗号分隔的目录列表。连接器通过对缓存块键进行哈希来选择一个目录，从而将文件分散到配置的路径中。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:94
msgid ""
"Use multiple paths when each path maps to an independent storage device "
"or mount point. For best results, keep every path visible to the LMCache "
"processes that need to retrieve the same chunks."
msgstr "当每个路径映射到独立的存储设备或挂载点时，请使用多个路径。为了获得最佳效果，请确保每个路径对需要检索相同块的 LMCache 进程可见。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:99
msgid "Legacy ``remote_url`` configuration"
msgstr "遗留 ``remote_url`` 配置"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:101
msgid ""
"The legacy ``remote_url`` form is still supported. The host and port are "
"parsed for compatibility with other remote URL formats; ``FSConnector`` "
"uses the path."
msgstr "遗留的 ``remote_url`` 形式仍然受到支持。主机和端口会被解析以兼容其他远程 URL 格式；``FSConnector`` 使用路径。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:116
msgid ""
"Prefer ``remote_storage_plugins`` for new deployments because it also "
"supports named instances and keeps connector-specific settings grouped by"
" plugin name."
msgstr "对于新的部署，优先使用 ``remote_storage_plugins``，因为它还支持命名实例，并将连接器特定的设置按插件名称分组。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:120
msgid "Optional settings"
msgstr "可选设置"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:122
msgid "The connector reads the following optional settings from ``extra_config``."
msgstr "连接器从 ``extra_config`` 中读取以下可选设置。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:124
msgid "``fs_connector_relative_tmp_dir``"
msgstr "``fs_connector_relative_tmp_dir``"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:125
msgid ""
"Relative directory used for temporary files before an atomic rename into "
"the final chunk path. The value must be relative, not absolute. When "
"omitted, temporary files are created next to the final file with a "
"``.tmp`` suffix."
msgstr "用于在原子重命名到最终块路径之前存放临时文件的相对目录。该值必须是相对的，而不是绝对的。当省略时，临时文件会在最终文件旁边创建，并带有 ``.tmp`` 后缀。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:129
msgid "``fs_connector_read_ahead_size``"
msgstr "``fs_connector_read_ahead_size``"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:130
msgid ""
"Number of bytes to read first when loading a chunk. If the read fills "
"that window, the connector reads the remaining bytes. This can trigger "
"filesystem readahead on filesystems that support it."
msgstr "加载块时首次读取的字节数。如果读取填满了该窗口，连接器将读取剩余的字节。这可能会触发支持的文件系统的预读取。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:134
msgid "``fs_connector_use_odirect``"
msgstr "``fs_connector_use_odirect``"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:135
msgid ""
"Enables ``O_DIRECT`` for aligned reads and writes on platforms that "
"expose it. The connector falls back to normal I/O when a chunk size is "
"not aligned to the filesystem block size. ``O_DIRECT`` is disabled "
"automatically when ``save_chunk_meta`` is enabled because the metadata "
"prefix is not block aligned."
msgstr "在支持的系统上启用 ``O_DIRECT`` 以进行对齐的读取和写入。当块大小未对齐到文件系统块大小时，连接器会回退到正常 I/O。当启用 ``save_chunk_meta`` 时，``O_DIRECT`` 会自动禁用，因为元数据前缀未对齐到块。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:141
msgid "``fs_base_path``"
msgstr "``fs_base_path``"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:142
msgid ""
"Compatibility fallback for plugin mode. Prefer "
"``remote_storage_plugin.<name>.base_path`` so the setting remains scoped "
"to a specific plugin instance."
msgstr "插件模式的兼容性回退。优先使用 ``remote_storage_plugin.<name>.base_path`` 以便将设置限制在特定的插件实例。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:146
msgid "Example with optional settings:"
msgstr "带可选设置的示例："

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:159
msgid "Operational notes"
msgstr "操作说明"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:161
msgid ""
"Ensure the LMCache process has permission to create directories and write"
" files under every configured base path."
msgstr "确保 LMCache 进程有权限在每个配置的基础路径下创建目录和写入文件。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:163
msgid ""
"Put the path on durable storage if cache reuse must survive process "
"restarts. Temporary directories such as ``/tmp`` are convenient for tests"
" but may be cleaned by the operating system."
msgstr "如果缓存重用必须在进程重启后仍然有效，请将路径放在持久存储上。像 ``/tmp`` 这样的临时目录方便用于测试，但可能会被操作系统清理。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:166
msgid ""
"Use the same mounted path for every process that should share cache "
"chunks. If one process writes to a private container path, other "
"processes will miss those chunks even if they use the same configuration "
"text."
msgstr "对于每个应该共享缓存块的进程，使用相同的挂载路径。如果一个进程写入了私有容器路径，其他进程将无法访问这些块，即使它们使用相同的配置文本。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:169
msgid ""
"Leave ``save_chunk_meta`` enabled when workers may infer different "
"metadata for the same chunk. Disable it only when you need the lower "
"overhead path and the workers share compatible cache metadata."
msgstr "当工作进程可能对相同块推理出不同的元数据时，请保持 ``save_chunk_meta`` 启用。仅在您需要更低开销路径且工作进程共享兼容的缓存元数据时才禁用它。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:172
msgid ""
"For MP mode L2 storage, see :doc:`../../mp/l2_storage`, which documents "
"the ``fs`` and ``fs_native`` L2 adapters configured through "
"``--l2-adapter``."
msgstr "有关 MP 模式 L2 存储的信息，请参见 :doc:`../../mp/l2_storage`，该文档介绍了通过 ``--l2-adapter`` 配置的 ``fs`` 和 ``fs_native`` L2 适配器。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:176
msgid "Minimal vLLM usage"
msgstr "最小 vLLM 使用方法"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:178
msgid ""
"After writing ``fs.yaml`` with one of the configurations above, start "
"vLLM with LMCache enabled:"
msgstr "在使用上述配置之一编写 ``fs.yaml`` 后，启动启用 LMCache 的 vLLM："

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/fs.rst:187
msgid ""
"Then send the same long-prefix request twice. The first request stores "
"chunks in the filesystem backend. The second request should report "
"LMCache hit tokens and load matching chunks from the configured "
"filesystem path."
msgstr "然后发送相同的长前缀请求两次。第一次请求将块存储在文件系统后端。第二次请求应报告 LMCache 命中令牌，并从配置的文件系统路径加载匹配的块。"

